rows.label: tev040501_SEL2021

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0001
rows.name: Prone live on port side of Ma-non ship.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0002
rows.name: Place used to be storeroom. It is still full of containers.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0003
rows.name: Containers also floating in air. It is big problem.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0004
rows.name:
Ma-non pass under containers without hitting heads.
But Prone are tall. Many heads bonked.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0005
rows.name: All Prone have bumps on head. Not just me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0008
rows.name:
You find treasure in unexpected places. Like nests.
Or beast droppings. Or strange trees.
Or insect mounds. Or others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0009
rows.name: You just need to look in right place.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0010
rows.name:
And when you find treasure, you take treasure.
Finder is keeper. It is profitable strategy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0016
rows.name:
No big problems. But sometimes Ma-non and Prone
argue.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0017
rows.name:
Ma-non are not bad aliens. But they talk all day.
Yammer all night. Prone find this annoying.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0018
rows.name:
If Prone talk too much, problem is solved with swift
punch to throat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0019
rows.name:
But we cannot punch puny Ma-non. Must hold back.
This makes us more annoyed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0020
rows.name: Life on alien ship is hard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0025
rows.name: I will tell you incredible thing![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0026
rows.name:
Some beasts "defend" against attacks.
Ganglion also do this.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0027
rows.name:
Do not hit them while they defend.
You will only waste Arts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0028
rows.name: ...What? Every BLADE knows this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0029
rows.name:
Hmm. Most Prone only think of offense.
Not "defense." I thought you might be same.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0035
rows.name: I led Earth aliens to safety.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0036
rows.name: I also closed this door before takeoff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0037
rows.name:
We were already lifting off. Situation was grave.
But I was chosen Door Closer. I did not flinch.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0038
rows.name:
All on Ma-non ship escaped without injury.
But I hear bad things happened in city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0045
rows.name: Yes. You can see them from here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0046
rows.name:
I could not read them. But Ma-non are wise.
They taught me what each one means.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0047
rows.name:
But I worry. Numbers are getting smaller.
They must be counting something bad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0048
rows.name:
What if it is how much food is left?
Soon day will come with no food at all.
I tremble to think about it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0055
rows.name: Did you know Cavern Clan fights with stolen weapons?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0056
rows.name: They took weapons from Earth aliens like you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0057
rows.name: Such actions shame all Prone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0058
rows.name: They should fight like true Prone. With fists![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0065
rows.name: Yes. You can see them from here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0066
rows.name:
I could not read them. But Ma-non are wise.
They taught me what each one means.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0067
rows.name:
They were going down. Then they stopped.
This made Earth aliens very happy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG0068
rows.name:
Maybe it showed how much food we had left?
I am glad we did not run out![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG1001
rows.name:
I share my watch duty with Prone named Naza
Tenpanzi.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG1002
rows.name:
But Naza always leaves to go on walks in New LA
park. Leaves me with work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG1003
rows.name:
Then she yells at me when I tell her to do job!
Said I am messing with vital mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG1004
rows.name:
"Mission" is probably to find store that sells delicious
meat. Hmph![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG2001
rows.name:
I was always mad at Naza Tenpanzi for leaving post.
She would go to park. Made me do work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG2002
rows.name:
But I was wrong. Naza had been chosen as
Protector of Great Tree![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG2003
rows.name:
Protector of Great Tree should not be sentry.
That is job for lunkhead![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev040501_MSG2004
rows.name:
Tell Naza I will keep watch here.
She and Orphean must work hard.
Bring Great Tree back to life.[ST:wait ]
